{"data":[{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 04/03/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Ra m\u1eaft phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi</h3>\r\nAnh em t\u1ea3i app m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y nha:\r\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xembongda.xemworldcup&hl=vi\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xembongda.xemworldcup&hl=vi</a>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-4-3-barca-danh-ao-so-7-cho-griezmann-c409a942583.html","id":"403"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 04/03/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 4/3: Barca d\u00e0nh \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Griezmann","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-942583\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-942583\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Barca d\u00e0nh \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Griezmann?</strong> T\u1edd AS cho bi\u1ebft n\u1ebfu (ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t khi) Antoine Griezmann r\u1eddi Atletico \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 c\u1ee7a CLB. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n Philippe Coutinho l\u1ea5y \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh cho Griezmann.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 4/3: Barca d\u00e0nh \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Griezmann - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\"  src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/skysports-antoine-griezmann-atletico-madrid-la-liga_4243441-660-1520095463-527-width660height495.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 495px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Antoine Griezmann</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Man City mua h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</strong>. Pep Guardiola trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n ng\u1eafn cho t\u1edd Telegraph cho bi\u1ebft trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y Man City s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o 1-2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mua \u00edt v\u00e0 mua r\u1ebb h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i\u201d, Pep n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Heynckes \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Lewandowski t\u1ea1m qu\u00ean Real.</strong> Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Robert Lewandowski s\u1ebd v\u1ec1 Real Madrid sau khi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ecfi Bayern Munich, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Jupp Heynckes \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quan \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan n\u00ean t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi g\u00e1c chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean. \u201cKhi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 cho Bayern th\u00ec anh ta ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho Bayern\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Si\u00eau c\u00f2 xui Donnarumma r\u1eddi Milan.</strong> Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n cho \u0111\u00e0i ph\u00e1t thanh Rai Sport \u1edf Italia, \u201csi\u00eau c\u00f2\u201d Mino Raiola b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Gianluigi Donnarumma d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u1edf l\u1ea1i AC Milan trong h\u00e8 2017 v\u1eabn n\u00ean r\u1eddi s\u00e2n San Siro \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u201cN\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00f3i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb r\u1ea5t h\u1eadu h\u0129nh cho Gigio\u201d, Raiola n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>VAR s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</strong> Ban ch\u1ea5p h\u00e0nh Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf IFAB \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ed th\u00f4ng qua quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 video tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i VAR s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho World Cup 2018. VAR \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Bundesliga, Serie A, MSL, gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Australia v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00fap \u1edf Anh, v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean IFAB. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FIFA Gianni Infantino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: \u201cS\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i trong th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u01b0ng VAR \u0111\u01b0a ch\u00fang ta t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u00f3 h\u01a1n\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/3: Pep g\u1ecdi Conte l\u00e0 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/1520079243-674-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 3/3: Pep g\u1ecdi Conte l\u00e0 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>HLV Pep Guardiola n\u1ee9c n\u1edf khen Conte tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City - Chelsea.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-4-3-barca-danh-ao-so-7-cho-griezmann-c409a942583.html","id":"402"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 03/03/2018 05:49 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-942434\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-942434\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>C\u1ef1u sao MU b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU, Paul Ince kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e0n em Paul Pogba h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City h\u01a1n MU. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p&nbsp;c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u00f2 m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao &amp;#34;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&amp;#34; b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Cuu-sao-paul-pogba-manchester-united_fx843m3kfmjo1vt7n8lnr-1520083678-973-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Pogba kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nu\u00f4ng chi\u1ec1u \u1edf MU</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>B\u00e1o nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Ibra cho MU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi HLV Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \"l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng\" Zlatan Ibrahimovic s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Manchester Evening News - t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng&nbsp;chuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn MU v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua Antoine Griezmann (Atletico Madrid), Mauro Icardi (Inter Milan), Ciro Immobile (Lazio) ho\u1eb7c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Liverpool ng\u0103n Kroos \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo&nbsp;chuy\u00ean gia Steve Nicol - ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool th\u00ec Real Madrid c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ea1nh h\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng b\u00e1n Toni Kroos cho MU l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean. Trong khi \u1ea5y, BL\u0110 \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Guillem Balague, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi&nbsp;T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt m\u00ed tin c\u1ef1c vui cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9&nbsp;MU&nbsp;v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a David De Gea. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean Sky Sports cho r\u1eb1ng De Gea s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" thay v\u00ec s\u1ebd sang Real Madrid h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"V\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a De Gea v\u00e0 Hazard. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;De Gea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man United. V\u1edbi Hazard, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t Galacticos m\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y,\"&nbsp;Balague cho hay tr\u00ean Sky Sports.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, De Gea t\u1eebng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.&nbsp;\"Th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua th\u1eadt nhanh. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 CLB \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 n\u0103m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i - t\u1ed1t c\u00f3 x\u1ea5u c\u00f3..., song t\u00f4i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i \u1edf ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u00f4i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 United tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n,\"&nbsp;th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Daily Star.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, theo Goal,&nbsp; De Gea s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 350.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, thay v\u00ec con s\u1ed1 275.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay De Gea</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \"D\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n h\u00e0 3.0\" v\u00e0 De Gea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng mi\u1ebfng gh\u00e9p quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 MU 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao &amp;#34;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&amp;#34; b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Mourinho-mua-thu-mon-dat-nhat-the-gioi-thay-De-Gea-660mu-stegen-1520048447-150-width660height441.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Ter Stegen \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. T\u1edd Goal ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, MU s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7 khi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Ter Stegen c\u1ee7a Barca 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tranh sao Napoli v\u1edbi Liverpool</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh. Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0o nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf Emre Can ch\u01b0a ch\u1ecbu gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu khoanh tay \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Carrick s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f2n Fellaini ra \u0111i. T\u1edd Daily Star cho hay, MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 gi\u00e1 Liverpool khi \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cu\u1ed7m si\u00eau trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti kh\u1ecfi Barca nh\u01b0 Neymar</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo t\u1edd The Sun, MU \u0111ang t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti, trng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford. Sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi HLV Mourinho. \u0110i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Umtiti v\u1edbi Barca tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch PSG \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar Junior m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017, v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao &amp;#34;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&amp;#34; b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Hoc-PSG-Neymar-cuom-sieu-trung-ve-cua-Barca-nintchdbpict000375417186-1520017284-65-width660height440.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: C\u1ef1u sao &amp;#34;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&amp;#34; b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khuy\u00ean Pogba \u0111\u1ebfn Man City - 4\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Umtiti l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shakhtar c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n SAO Brazil cho MU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Fred \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Carrick v\u00e0 Fellaini. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 MU m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00e0 Man City c\u0169ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 25 n\u00e0y. T\u1edd Manchester Evening News cho hay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ukraine \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n Fred cho MU do \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Marcos Rojo h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf MU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u do di ch\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Rojo, t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Sporting Lisbon n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Argentina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Old Trafford v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi Fellaini</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eeba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, MU s\u1eafp m\u1ea5t Marouane Fellaini ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Sau 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110 MU. Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, c\u00f3 tin Arsenal t\u1eebng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Fellaini nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi, \u201c\u0110\u1ea7u x\u00f9\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Darmian \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1ec1 Juventus</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo Football Italia, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00e0 ph\u00eda Juventus \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi MU, Darmian thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Torino, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Turin. D\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia kh\u00e1c, Darmian v\u1eabn \u01b0u ti\u00ean tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Bom t\u1ea5n Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU: Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, kh\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n Gareth Bale\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-02/news_176770_1-640x480-1519932223-593-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Bom t\u1ea5n Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU: Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, kh\u1ecfi c\u1ea7n Gareth Bale</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>K\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arjen Robben, MU s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam Gareth Bale.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-hoc-psg-neymar-cuom-sieu-trung-ve-cua-barca-c409a942434.html","id":"401"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 03/03/2018 05:49 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 3/3: Conte ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5t tay v\u1edbi Guardiola & Man City","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-942435\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-942435\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Conte ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5t tay v\u1edbi Guardiola v\u00e0 Man City. </strong>\u1ede v\u00f2ng 28 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Chelsea thua \u0111au tr\u00ean s\u00e2n MU, qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi top 4. HLV Antonio Conte k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00ecnh sinh v\u1edbi Man City ngay t\u1ea1i Etihad v\u00e0o 23h ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt, 4/3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 3/3: Conte ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5t tay v\u1edbi Guardiola &amp; Man City - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-3-3-Conte-choi-tat-tay-voi-Guardiola-antonio-conte-pep-guardiola-cropped_1js6kh8wxa7wd1-1520019045-803-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Conte quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Guardiola</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lewandowski mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Real.</strong> Theo t\u1edd Marca, Robert Lewandowski ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Bayern Munich. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Matt Hummels v\u00e0 t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Allianz Arena trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Ngo\u00e0i ra, MU c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u201cLewy\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Napoli v\u00e0 HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ednh ph\u1ee5c. </strong>M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 n\u00e0y, Napoli d\u00f9 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Naples hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Serie A, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Juventus 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1 tr\u1eadn. Hai HLV h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 Maurico Pochettino c\u00f9ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 m\u00e0 HLV Sarri v\u00e0 Napoli l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Balotelli s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</strong> H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Mario Balotelli v\u00e0 CLB Nice s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u1edf l\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Balotelli mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. \u201cNg\u1ef1a ch\u1ee9ng\u201d t\u1eebng 2 l\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay Wenger.</strong> Theo t\u1edd London Standard, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng thay th\u1ebf HLV Arsene Wenger t\u1ea1i Arsenal l\u00e0 HLV Leonardo Jardim. T\u1ea1i Monaco, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho r\u1eb1ng HLV 43 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y th\u1eeba k\u1ebf nh\u1eefng tinh hoa c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger th\u1eddi tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Barcelona kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng s\u00e2n bay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea1m \u201dVua\u201d Messi\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-03/sport-preview-messis-house-and-barcelona-airport-640x480-1520014756-304-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Barcelona kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng s\u00e2n bay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea1m \u201dVua\u201d Messi</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>\u1ede x\u1ee9 Catalunya, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina Messi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ho\u00e0ng.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-3-3-conte-choi-tat-tay-voi-guardiola-man-city-c409a942435.html","id":"400"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 02/03/2018 05:42 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2/3: S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Bayern ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai James Rodriguez","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-942158\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-942158\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Bayern ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai James Rodriguez.</strong> Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Karl-Heinz Rummenigge v\u1eeba ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 2 m\u00f9a t\u1eeb Real Madrid. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t James ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m sau m\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 2/3: S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Bayern ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai James Rodriguez - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-01/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-2-3-Sep-lon-Bayern-tiet-lo-tuong-lai-James-Rodriguez-59e335002ee40f5012000001-1519922603-433-width660height373.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">James Rodriguez v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Bayern</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mua h\u00e0ng Southampton.</strong> Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, Liverpool \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Southampton cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mario Lemina. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool. Lemina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Naby Keita - ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield t\u1eeb RB Leipzig. T\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 6/2014 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 mua 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb Southampton.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lukaku \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.</strong> Romelu Lukaku c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u1eafn ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i New York, M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ed5 Brooklyn Nets. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf MU \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ed5 n\u00e0y ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n, coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00ecnh Brooklyn Nets. C\u0169ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Lukaku \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 NBA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mkhitaryan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Mourinho.</strong> Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City, t\u00e2n binh Henrikh Mkhitaryan c\u1ee7a Arsenal ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i MU. Theo \u201cMicky\u201d, anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 MU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Liverpool l\u00e3i kh\u1ee7ng.</strong> BL\u0110 Liverpool v\u1eeba c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn 39 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong t\u00e0i kh\u00f3a 2016/17. Doanh thu c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u0103ng 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3, \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ed1c 364 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield c\u00f2n l\u00e3i kh\u1ee7ng h\u01a1n sau khi b\u00e1n Philippe Coutinho.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"\u201dBom t\u1ea5n\u201d Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU: S\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Ibra hay ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 ki\u1ec3u Owen?\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-28/mu1-1519813957-751-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">\u201dBom t\u1ea5n\u201d Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU: S\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Ibra hay ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 ki\u1ec3u Owen?</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU gi\u00e1 \"0 \u0111\u1ed3ng\", Mourinho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-2-3-sep-lon-bayern-tiet-lo-tuong-lai-james-rodriguez-c409a942158.html","id":"399"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 02/03/2018 00:46 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Kane b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda Real, Mourinho xu\u1ed1ng tay 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-942163\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-942163\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Kane b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda Real, Mourinho xu\u1ed1ng tay 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Harry Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez cho \"D\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n h\u00e0 3.0\". Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Tottenham nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Real c\u00f2n v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1eef d\u1ed9i \u1edf n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho hay, Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kane.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Kane b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda Real, Mourinho xu\u1ed1ng tay 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-02/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Kane-bi-cam-cua-Real-Mourinho-xuong-tay-200-trieu-bang-mu-kane-1519926223-570-width660height470.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Sanchez v\u00e0 Kane s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1eed v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady, MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua. Diario Gol \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng b\u00e0i c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid. T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y cho hay MU c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \"Los Blancos\". \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o n\u00ean 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, Kane \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u0169ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Herrera c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 Atletico Madrid</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i MU. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady, Herrera \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Theo t\u1edd El Gol Digital, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bilbao s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Herrera ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 n\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \"Kluivert con\" s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ajax</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Si\u00eau c\u00f2 Mino Raiola v\u1eeba th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin kh\u00f4ng vui cho MU. Justin Kluivert \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Ajax. Con trai c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Patrick Kluivert \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 18 n\u00ean MU v\u00e0 Barca c\u00f9ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, Justin kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m, anh c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i Ajax tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed5i gi\u00e1 Umtiti l\u00ean 60 tri\u1ec7u euro</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MU \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Barca r\u1ea5t b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Samuel Umtiti. HLV Mourinho r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi. T\u1edd Goal cho hay, MU ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean 60 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f9ng cam k\u1ebft m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Umtiti h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Barca. V\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f2i Barca k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c th\u00f9 lao 160.000 euro/tu\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"\u201dBom t\u1ea5n\u201d Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU: S\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Ibra hay ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 ki\u1ec3u Owen?\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-28/mu1-1519813957-751-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">\u201dBom t\u1ea5n\u201d Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU: S\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Ibra hay ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 ki\u1ec3u Owen?</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Robben \u0111\u1ebfn MU gi\u00e1 \"0 \u0111\u1ed3ng\", Mourinho s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-kane-bi-cam-cua-real-mourinho-xuong-tay-200-trieu-bang-c409a942163.html","id":"398"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 01/03/2018 01:35 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1/3: Arsenal \u0111\u1ea5u Man City d\u1ec5 ho\u00e3n v\u00ec \u201cQu\u00e1i v\u1eadt\u201d","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-941910\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-941910\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Tr\u1eadn Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n v\u00ec \u201cQu\u00e1i v\u1eadt ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng\u201d: </strong>Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, \u0111\u1ee3t gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1nh b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i tr\u00ean l\u00e3nh th\u1ed5 to\u00e0n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi t\u00ean g\u1ecdi \u201cQu\u00e1i v\u1eadt ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng\u201d \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London (Anh qu\u1ed1c) ch\u00ecm trong b\u00e3o tuy\u1ebft.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1/3: Arsenal \u0111\u1ea5u Man City d\u1ec5 ho\u00e3n v\u00ec \u201cQu\u00e1i v\u1eadt\u201d - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-01/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-1-3-Arseal-dau-Man-City-de-hoan-vi-Quai-vat-hot-1-1519840327-267-width660height452.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Thierry Henry tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1eeda s\u00e2n Emirates c\u1ee7a Arsenal hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y tuy\u1ebft tr\u1eafng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1eb7t s\u00e2n Emirates - s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111ang ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u0103ng tuy\u1ebft. D\u00f9 BTC s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng d\u00f9ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng l\u00f2 s\u01b0\u1edfi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tan b\u0103ng nh\u01b0ng hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City \u1edf v\u00f2ng 28 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00fac 2h45 ng\u00e0y 2/3 t\u1edbi (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam) v\u1eabn l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p. Nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn n\u00e0y b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Arsenal 3-0 \u1edf Wembley \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u1ea1t c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ronaldinho khuy\u00ean Kane \u201cb\u1ecf t\u1ed1i theo s\u00e1ng\u201d:</strong> Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Mirror, theo huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Harry Kane n\u00ean r\u1eddi Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay nh\u01b0 Real Madrid, Barcelona hay Manchester City,...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\u201cHarry Kane gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa khi m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m l\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Barcelona, Real Madrid hay Man City m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.\u201d</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Van Gaal ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mourinho b\u1ea1c t\u00ecnh: </strong>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean SportBild, HLV Louis Van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u00f4ng k\u00edch Jose Mourinho v\u00ec c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Bastian Schweinsteiger. Theo \"Tulip th\u00e9p\",&nbsp;Schweini l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t ngo\u00e0i tu\u1ed5i 30.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Enrique m\u01a1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ed5i Hazard l\u1ea5y Bale: </strong>Theo El Chiringuito, c\u1ef1u HLV Barcelona - Luis Enrique hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Antonio Conte v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u201cThe Blues\u201d chi ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Gareth Bale (Real Madrid). C\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft \u201cK\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng\u201d s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y Eden Hazard.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef:</strong> H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nacho Monreal v\u1eeba d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 2-4 tu\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn Arsenal l\u00e2m nguy v\u00ec s\u1ebd v\u1eafng anh trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Man City v\u00e0 Watford \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng hay g\u1eb7p AC Milan \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Europa League.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Man City t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u \u201dm\u1ed3i ngon\u201d Arsenal: Pep ch\u1ecdn ng\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-03-01/640pep1-1519839037-321-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Man City t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u \u201dm\u1ed3i ngon\u201d Arsenal: Pep ch\u1ecdn ng\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>HLV Guardiola tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n khi t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal \u1edf v\u00f2ng 28 Premier League.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-1-3-arsenal-dau-man-city-de-hoan-vi-quai-vat-c409a941910.html","id":"397"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 01/03/2018 00:02 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Real tr\u1ea3 De Gea 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Messi \"t\u00e1i m\u1eb7t\"","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-941904\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-941904\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Real tr\u1ea3 De Gea 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Messi \"t\u00e1i m\u1eb7t\"</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111ang r\u1ed1t r\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \"D\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n h\u00e0 3.0\". B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, \u00f4ng tr\u00f9m 70 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e2m n\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 De Gea. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Don Balon, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi con s\u1ed1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 27 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Real tr\u1ea3 De Gea 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Messi &amp;#34;t\u00e1i m\u1eb7t&amp;#34; - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-28/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Real-tra-De-Gea-88-trieu-bang-Messi-mu-degea-1519836350-883-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">De Gea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn MU v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Barca lo l\u1eafng. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh cho hay, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Ter Stegen, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Barca thay th\u1ebf. Ter Stegen \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 15 tr\u1eadn gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi sau 25 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i La Liga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu De Gea \u0111\u1ebfn Real, Messi s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd Manchester Everning News (MEN) ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 HLV Mourinho s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU. Si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp. M\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn Mourinho c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 s\u1edbm nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n CR7 l\u1ea5y MU l\u00e0m v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng y\u00eau s\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Young v\u00e0 Blind s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong vi\u1ec7c x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i MU. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb MEN cho hay, Young v\u00e0 Blind s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford sau khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Quy\u1ebft ph\u00e1 Chelsea v\u1ee5 SAO Napoli</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Conte \u0111ang nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Elseid Hysaj c\u1ee7a Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, ESPN ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 MU c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c. HLV Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1edfi Valenica \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n Shaw ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf Hysaj s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, MU v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Chelsea n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neville mu\u1ed1n Martial ra \u0111i</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville v\u1eeba c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh khi\u1ebfn fan MU b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 2 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t nghi ng\u1edd t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial t\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Neville cho r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU \u2013 Mourinho n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng: H\u1ea5t c\u1eb3ng Rashford, mua SAO Serie A\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-28/gettyimages-839569770-640-1519809726-587-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU \u2013 Mourinho n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng: H\u1ea5t c\u1eb3ng Rashford, mua SAO Serie A</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Rashford c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb MU thanh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Serie A.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-real-tra-de-gea-88-trieu-bang-messi-tai-mat-c409a941904.html","id":"396"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 28/02/2018 04:02 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 28/2: Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch VIP th\u0103m nh\u00e0, h\u1eb9n l\u1ecbch giao \u0111\u1ea5u","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-941654\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-941654\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch VIP th\u0103m nh\u00e0, h\u1eb9n l\u1ecbch giao \u0111\u1ea5u: </strong>Tr\u00ean Twitter c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u0110B\u0110 Argentina \u2013 Claudio Tapia \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eeba khoe b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh gh\u00e9 th\u0103m nh\u00e0 <strong>Lionel Messi</strong> \u1edf Barcelona v\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y 2 b\u1ee9c tranh v\u1ec1 anh v\u00e0 \u201cAlbiceleste\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 28/2: Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch VIP th\u0103m nh\u00e0, h\u1eb9n l\u1ecbch giao \u0111\u1ea5u - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-28/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-28-2-Messi-duoc-khach-VIP-tham-nha-hen-lich-giao-dau-messi-1519757102-734-width660height502.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Messi vui v\u1ebb nh\u1eadn hai b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u0110B\u0110 Argentina trao t\u1eb7ng khi \u0111\u1ebfn th\u0103m nh\u00e0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C\u0169ng nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Tapia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng <em>Messi </em>thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c b\u00ean t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Catalunya t\u1ea1i Barcelona tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0y (m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>M\u1eb7c d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, Wenger v\u1eabn \u201cch\u00e0y c\u1ed1i\u201d \u0111\u00f2i tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Arsenal: </strong>T\u1edd Daily Mail cho hay, HLV Arsene Wenger kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi b\u1ecf \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay sau khi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba thua th\u1ea3m 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Anh. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d l\u00e0 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m 2019.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Em trai Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Madrid: </strong>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha loan tin, c\u1ea3 Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Sevilla \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chung l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thorgan Hazard. \u1ede Bundesliga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu em trai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Eden Hazard \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay khi \u0111\u00e3 ghi 8 b\u00e0n sau 26 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Borussia Monchengladbach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Buffon \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd, t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u0110T \u00dd \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina v\u00e0 Anh: </strong>D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 40 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Italia tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng play-off tranh v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Gianluigi Buffon c\u1ee7a Juventus l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T Italia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo \u201cl\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng\u201d n\u00e0y, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n giao th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u201cAzzurri\u201d v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n khi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o thi\u00ean thanh \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 Anh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 23/3 v\u00e0 27/3 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Usain Bolt \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i Ng\u00f4i sao th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: </strong>C\u1ef1u sao \u0111i\u1ec1n kinh ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat&nbsp;Usain Bolt x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn g\u00e2y qu\u1ef9 t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n g\u1eb7p C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10/6 t\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u2013 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a MU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>UEFA x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea1t c\u1ef1u sao Man City:&nbsp;</strong>L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (UEFA) v\u1eeba ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn treo gi\u00f2 Nasri 6 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho Man City d\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00ednh v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5m.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 27/2: L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay HLV Wenger t\u1ea1i Arsenal\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-27/640x480-1519726842-487-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 27/2: L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay HLV Wenger t\u1ea1i Arsenal</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft League Cup.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-28-2-messi-duoc-khach-vip-tham-nha-hen-lich-giao-dau-c409a941654.html","id":"395"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 27/02/2018 01:08 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 27/2: Real ch\u1edb d\u1ea1i b\u00e1n Bale mua Hazard","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-941405\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-941405\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Real ch\u1edb d\u1ea1i b\u00e1n Bale mua Hazard:</strong> \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Bale v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c Bale \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Real kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u00e1n Bale, d\u00f9 Hazard c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Zidane v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i\u201d, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Real, Alvaro Arbeloa n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zidane c\u1ea7u ch\u00fac Neymar s\u1edbm b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.</strong> M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Zidane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi an \u1ee7i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil sau khi hay tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng vui n\u1ebfu Neymar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Hi v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng (\u0111\u1ea5u&nbsp;Real \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8&nbsp;Champions League). T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 27/2: Real ch\u1edb d\u1ea1i b\u00e1n Bale mua Hazard - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-27/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-27-2-Zidane-cau-chuc-Neymar-som-binh-phuc-hot2-1519665852-614-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Zidane c\u1ea7u ch\u00fac Neymar s\u1edbm b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal. </strong>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, Thierry Henry nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t. \"V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Wenger, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Carabao Cup. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua t\u1ea1i Champions League hay Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.\u201d</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>B\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap McTominay cao v\u1ecdt 25cm trong 18 th\u00e1ng</strong>. T\u1edd Daily Mail ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Scott McTominay \u0111\u00e3 cao v\u1ecdt th\u00eam 25cm ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 18 th\u00e1ng qua. C\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a McTominay v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u0103ng l\u00ean 88 kg. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, McTominay \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao anh l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao. \"Hai HLV Warren Joyce v\u00e0 Paul McGuinness \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd kh\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd l\u1ea1i cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\u201d</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho coi tr\u1ecdng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Liverpool.</strong> Trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Chelsea. \"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0o v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi MU. Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool lu\u00f4n mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea, Lingard nh\u1eadn tin vui.</strong> V\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea, Lingard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady, BL\u0110 MU \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho anh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1n 100.000 b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng cao trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i mua SAO Real 700 tri\u1ec7u euro\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-27/1519665399-453-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i mua SAO Real 700 tri\u1ec7u euro</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Theo t\u1edd Diario Gol, Mourinho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn Man City v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-27-2-real-cho-dai-ban-bale-mua-hazard-c409a941405.html","id":"394"}]}